title: Sel Sel Lyrics Kaakk Muttai Song Lyrics
stanzas:
Kaakka Muttai Sel Sel Song Lyrics
Singer(s): Sathya Prakash
Music: GV Prakash,

Chal chalae 
chal chalae chal chal.
chare chal chalae
chal chalae chal.

Chal chalae chal chalae
siragai virithu sel.
Chal chalae chal chalae
kaattril yaeri sel.

Po po, vazhve
kaakkaa mutta thaan.
kottai vittae 
potta satta thaan.

Mazhai veyil 
rendum engal 
annan thambi thaan.
Natchathiram varuvadhu
nammai nambi thaan.

ingae vali yaavum
nerillai sandhula 
pondhula po po 
po poda po poda
pudhu inbam thaedi po
kanpaarkkum yaavum
un sondham endrenni po
innum melae po. 

Thooral vandhaalingae
koni kudaiyaagumey.
oru quater bottle-lai
vilakkaai maattri
iruttai ottiduvom.

Ada kattaandharayil
kaigalai neetti 
paduththadhum
thoongiduvom.

Sandaigal adithadi 
ingum undu
naal thorumey.

Sattena anbaai
anaithida odum 
nam nenjamaey.

kadhavugal undu
mugavari illai 
nam veedhiyilae.

ada yaar veedum
nam veedu ena enni
vazhugirom po po
po  poda po poda
pudhu inbam thaedi po
kanpaarkkum yaavum
un sondham endrenni po
innum melae po. 

Touser dhapaal petti
dhosthu aattu kutti.
dhinam anjae rupaai
kidachaa podhum
hero naangaladaa.

ada anjaan class-a
thaandala, aanaa
anubavam adhigamadaa.

koovam enbadhai 
saakkadai endru
yaar sonnadhadaa.

koovam engalai 
thaai madiyaaga
thaalaattumadaaa.

rathiri engal 
kachchaerikku
vandugal paadumadaa
ada ration card 
adhil engal 
naai per serthiduvom. 

po po 
po  poda po poda
pudhu inbam thaedi po
kanpaarkkum yaavum
un sondham endrenni po
innum melae po. 


Chal chalae chal chalae
siragai virithu sel.
Chal chalae chal chalae
kaattril yaeri sel.
